headline: 2 Reasons to Like ADP (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: ADP has had an impressive run over the past six months. While the S&P 500 has been flat, the stock has returned 7% and now trades at $296.12. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
